  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No fear of domination by pay-to-win players, just plenty of free benefits, easy socialization, and strategic combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Introduction</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.Game Background</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a fantasy world of swords and magic, where continents of different times and civilizations intertwine. Legend has it that in ancient times, demons roamed freely. To save humanity, the gods used their last strength to expel the demons from Yggdrasil, leaving behind magical crystals to protect the land from demonic invasion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As time passed, the power of the crystals gradually faded. When the crystal's light dimmed, the first summoners built the Summoner's Academy around it, deciding to protect their home with human strength alone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Centuries later, an evil summoner, having strayed from the path, destroyed the academy and sought to use the academy's crystal to summon demons again. In a final effort, the academy head decided to shatter the crystal, issuing a command to all summoners in the world to protect the crystal of the academy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a novice summoner just starting out. Fate has led you to obtain the first shard of the academy's crystal. The overture to adventure has been written. The rest of the story is yours to write...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.Game Features</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reject pay-to-win, sign in for diamonds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automatic combat, say no to grinding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Humorous storyline, hilarious dialogues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adorable heroes, open continuous draws.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exquisite character designs, enjoyable collection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple growth paths, easy cultivation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diverse dungeons, varied gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/cc5029a7a47552c6143081d6bd9de4ae.poster.avif?t=1764141237\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/cc5029a7a47552c6143081d6bd9de4ae.webm?t=1764141237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/cc5029a7a47552c6143081d6bd9de4ae.mp4?t=1764141237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3.Gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Main storyline dungeons, battles, and narrative progression, spirit collection and cultivation, strategic combat combinations.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/346226021c51fb8d0e74b2ca7f449eab.poster.avif?t=1764141237\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/346226021c51fb8d0e74b2ca7f449eab.webm?t=1764141237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/346226021c51fb8d0e74b2ca7f449eab.mp4?t=1764141237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Light Roguelike treasure hunting and maze gameplay.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/ccfc938a558a22076f890a02ce628401.poster.avif?t=1764141237\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/ccfc938a558a22076f890a02ce628401.webm?t=1764141237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/ccfc938a558a22076f890a02ce628401.mp4?t=1764141237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various PVE dungeons and PVP challenge modes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/bc479aaaf3991fd8caf694a0d90facd1.poster.avif?t=1764141237\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/bc479aaaf3991fd8caf694a0d90facd1.webm?t=1764141237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/bc479aaaf3991fd8caf694a0d90facd1.mp4?t=1764141237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/5c1378276afdaaf36e481e6f208f03f5.poster.avif?t=1764141237\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/5c1378276afdaaf36e481e6f208f03f5.webm?t=1764141237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/5c1378276afdaaf36e481e6f208f03f5.mp4?t=1764141237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player socialization: friends, guilds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fantasy homeland system: home building, player interaction.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/02bd5851f6b3c5ccf4d1fc41d53807f8.poster.avif?t=1764141237\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/02bd5851f6b3c5ccf4d1fc41d53807f8.webm?t=1764141237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/02bd5851f6b3c5ccf4d1fc41d53807f8.mp4?t=1764141237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Phantom beast system: hatch phantom beasts to aid in battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/c816a5cf16c035d4c1a628d2858ff395.poster.avif?t=1764141237\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/c816a5cf16c035d4c1a628d2858ff395.webm?t=1764141237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/c816a5cf16c035d4c1a628d2858ff395.mp4?t=1764141237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No fear of domination by pay-to-win players, just plenty of free benefits, easy socialization, and strategic combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Introduction</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.Game Background</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a fantasy world of swords and magic, where continents of different times and civilizations intertwine. Legend has it that in ancient times, demons roamed freely. To save humanity, the gods used their last strength to expel the demons from Yggdrasil, leaving behind magical crystals to protect the land from demonic invasion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As time passed, the power of the crystals gradually faded. When the crystal's light dimmed, the first summoners built the Summoner's Academy around it, deciding to protect their home with human strength alone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Centuries later, an evil summoner, having strayed from the path, destroyed the academy and sought to use the academy's crystal to summon demons again. In a final effort, the academy head decided to shatter the crystal, issuing a command to all summoners in the world to protect the crystal of the academy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a novice summoner just starting out. Fate has led you to obtain the first shard of the academy's crystal. The overture to adventure has been written. The rest of the story is yours to write...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.Game Features</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reject pay-to-win, sign in for diamonds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automatic combat, say no to grinding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Humorous storyline, hilarious dialogues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adorable heroes, open continuous draws.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exquisite character designs, enjoyable collection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple growth paths, easy cultivation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diverse dungeons, varied gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/cc5029a7a47552c6143081d6bd9de4ae.poster.avif?t=1764141237\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/cc5029a7a47552c6143081d6bd9de4ae.webm?t=1764141237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/cc5029a7a47552c6143081d6bd9de4ae.mp4?t=1764141237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3.Gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Main storyline dungeons, battles, and narrative progression, spirit collection and cultivation, strategic combat combinations.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/346226021c51fb8d0e74b2ca7f449eab.poster.avif?t=1764141237\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/346226021c51fb8d0e74b2ca7f449eab.webm?t=1764141237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/346226021c51fb8d0e74b2ca7f449eab.mp4?t=1764141237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Light Roguelike treasure hunting and maze gameplay.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/extras/ccfc938a558a22076f890a02ce628401.poster.avif?t=1764141237\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850220/e